CustomField.description: This field indicates that no match was found for the contact's email domain when they self-registered for access to the extranet. When checked, this field will send out a rejection notice to the contact. This field should not be checked manually. It's only checked by automation when a user / contact self-registers for access to the extranet.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This field indicates that no match was found for the contact's email domain when they self-registered for access to the extranet. When checked, this field will send out a rejection notice to the contact. This field should not be checked manually.
CustomField.label: No Matching Domain
